  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It had-- he had-- wear red here, velvet on the-- anyway, a doctor that I knew very well that was-- Kleinbaum was his name, Moshe Kleinbaum.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He-- he subsequently was in Israel and his name was Sneh.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The people-- S-N-E-H, Sneh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we went to my, my in-laws.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You-- myself, [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Zonya ?] and myself, we stayed with the in-laws-- went to home to my parents and found everybody in good shape.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And started the Soviet with-- on the way-- on the way as we passed [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Bug ?], we learned that Ribbentrop and Molotov made an agreement to divide Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we found ourselves in the Russian part of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, well, we saw people with red something around their arms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so there we are.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] People are alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They prefer what is-- the war-- the war doesn't exist anymore because this part is the Russian protection.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was the Russians that liberated us, supposedly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that started the time of the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My father-in-law hated the, the Reds, just plain hated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was a Russian, Russian, Russian-born and a Russian officer in the Czar's Army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So he was not happy about the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I cannot say whether I was happy or unhappy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The fact is, there we were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were out of war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We are not in any danger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Since-- the things, we left in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And on the way-- because I couldn't carry much, I'd throw things out and throw things out just to-- less to carry.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we walked nights.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Sometimes [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Zonya ?] was keeping my-- my rucksack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we were walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I was almost walking asleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And in daytime, it was like sport.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
